Folder Name = always small letter

Class Name/File Name = pascal case
    eg., MyNameIsSabari, IAmWorkingOnIntellij

Method Name = camel case
    eg., myNameIsSabari, runningTheJavaProgram

Variable Name = camel case
    eg., demoSite, practiceCount

    Local Variable --> camel case --> eg., programmingLanguage
    Global Variable --> pascal case --> eg., ProgrammingLanguage
    Global Variable (Final Variables - value cannot be change) - eg., PI = 3.14 --> PROGRAMMING_VALUE (snake case in full capital)